---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="Reflection | HCI Portfolio">
    <PageHeader 
        title="Reflection" 
        subtitle="Looking back on what we learned and what's next."
    />

    <Section title="Challenges & Solutions">
        <div class="space-y-12">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Balancing Fun & Function</h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                    One of the biggest challenges was ensuring the game elements didn't distract from the core educational content. We solved this by using gamification as a wrapper rather than the content itself.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Accessibility</h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Ensuring the high-contrast "Neo-Brutalist" style remained accessible required careful color selection and testing.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Section>

    <Section title="Future Improvements" class="bg-neutral-900/20 border-t border-neutral-800">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Mobile App</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Developing a native mobile version for better on-the-go access.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Social Features</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Adding community features for students to connect.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">AI Integration</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Personalized study plans using AI recommendations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Section>
</Layout>
